 
 Build a  Rest api using node.js sequelize mysql2.

 Project name:Bank user details

1)Create our own user as Sudo code.
-----------------------------------

sudo mysql
select User,host from mysql.user;
CREATE USER 'NAVEEN'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED by 'Naveen123';

2)grant all the privileges.
---------------------------

GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES;
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

3)Login from the created user.
------------------------------

user:mysql -u NAVEEN -p
Password:

4)create a databse:
------------------

CREATE DATABASE NAVEENDB;
SHOW DATABASE;

